# COVID-19 Global Data Analysis | Power BI

## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview
This project analyzes global COVID-19 trends using day-to-day country-wise data.  
The goal is to explore confirmed cases, deaths, recoveries, and active cases over time and present insights through an interactive Power BI dashboard.

The analysis focuses on:
- Time-series trends of COVID-19 cases
- Country-wise comparison of confirmed, deaths, and recovery rates
- Identification of highly impacted regions

---

## ğŸ—‚ Dataset
**Source:** Public COVID-19 global dataset  
**File Used:** `full_grouped.csv`

### Key Columns:
- Date  
- Country/Region  
- Confirmed  
- Deaths  
- Recovered  
- Active  
- New cases  
- New deaths  

The dataset contains daily COVID-19 statistics across multiple countries.

